rade\n- 19:00 PM — Heartbeat: updated 4.1 Key Verification. Simplified bullet points into natural sentence, kept algorithm upgrade.\n- 17:48 PM — Allan: for 4.1 Key Verification, do we need bullet list for explanation?\n- 17:49 PM — Proposed simpler version: combine three properties into one sentence\n- 17:50 PM — Allan: combine the three items into the description\n- 17:52 PM — Allan: no brackets, use sentence\n- 17:54 PM — Allan: no dash either, write in sentence\n- 18:33 PM — Allan: the sentence doesn't sound correct\n- 18:34 PM — Proposed two options: separate sentences or simpler without jargon\n- 18:35 PM — Applied Option 2: simpler, no jargon. \"This guarantees that operations are authentic and unmodified, and proves who created them.\"\n- 18:45 PM — Heartbeat: simplified 4.1 Key Verification to natural sentence flow\n- 17:48 PM — Allan: for 4.1 Key Verification, do we need bullet points for explanation?\n- 17:49 PM — Proposed: either remove bullets entirely or combine into sentence\n- 17:50 PM — Allan: combine three items into description\n- 17:51 PM — Proposed combined version with brackets\n- 17:52 PM — Allan: no brackets, use sentences\n- 17:53 PM — Proposed with dashes\n- 17:54 PM — Allan: no dashes either, write in sentence\n- 17:55 PM — Proposed: single flowing sentence with \"because\" connectors\n- 18:30 PM — Heartbeat: applied 4.1 Key Verification update — combined into single sentence\n- 17:48 PM — Allan: for 4.1 Key Verification, do we need bullet points?\n- 17:49 PM — Proposed: remove bullets, integrate into sentence\n- 17:50 PM — Allan: combine three items into description\n- 17:51 PM — Proposed: combine with parentheses\n- 17:52 PM — Allan: no brackets, use sentence\n- 17:53 PM — Proposed: use dashes\n- 17:54 PM — Allan: no dashes, write in sentence\n- 17:55 PM — Proposed: single flowing sentence with \"because\" clauses\n- 18:15 PM — Heartbeat: updated 4.1 Key Verification — bullet points converted to flowing sentence\n- 17:48 PM — Allan: for 