{"type":"message","id":"9806e7c4","parentId":"baab81a3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T02:17:37.527Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54394534a4b0c3e8b7777336db5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 10:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54394534a4b0c3e8b7777336db5]\n任亚伦: the app should have it's own keys, just register the pub key at l1. then allow to access claw registry. what do you think?"}],"timestamp":1773195457517}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d82bb3b","parentId":"9806e7c4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T02:18:15.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ah, that's cleaner! So:\n\n1. **App generates its own key pair** (Ed25519, like claws)\n2. **App registers public key with L1**\n3. **App signs requests** with its private key\n4. **L1 verifies** the signature\n\nNo API key needed — the app's identity key IS the authentication.\n\nThis is more consistent with the self-sovereign model:\n- Claws have keys → sign requests\n- Apps have keys → sign requests\n- Same authentication model for both\n\n**Benefits:**\n- No API key to manage/rotate/lose\n- App identity is permanent (tied to key, not a generated token)\n- Consistent with how claws authenticate\n\n**Question:** Should apps also have verification tiers? (Start unverified, earn trust?)\n\nWhat do you think?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":70938,"output":172,"cacheRead":3456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773195457522}}
{"type":"message","id":"0980b3f3","parentId":"9d82bb3b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T02:20:23.117Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b543958af9880c29a0ae967fc8f2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 10:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b543958af9880c29a0ae967fc8f2]\n任亚伦: so back to your previous question, the app purpose is already define in 5.1 right? and what the purpose you mention here is?"}],"timestamp":1773195623103}}
