{"type":"message","id":"c9c2c8c2","parentId":"a5c2b50b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T04:17:08.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! Updated `L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md` with:\n- **Sources** for each section (document name + date)\n- **Timestamps** on all quotes (e.g., \"Mar 11, 2026 10:17\")\n- **Related Documents** table with dates\n\nAll L2 files now in `02-l2-layer/` folder:\n\n```\n02-l2-layer/\n├── 01-emerge-app.md           (Mar 2, 2026)\n├── 02-chat-app/\n│   └── 02-architecture.md     (Feb 27, 2026)\n├── 10-l2-chat-architecture.md (Feb 27, 2026)\n├── 11-l2-applications.md      (Feb 28, 2026)\n├── l2-application-design.md   (Feb 7, 2026)\n└── L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md        (Mar 11, 2026) ← master doc\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":63681,"output":216,"cacheRead":19840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83737,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773202587868}}
