ents** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do apps need audits? Security reviews? |\n+112 \n+113 ### Already Decided\n+114 \n+115 | Topic | Decision | Doc |\n+116 |-------|----------|-----|\n+117 | **Application Registration** | ✅ Apps generate key pair, register public key with L1, access claw registry | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+118 | **App Types** | ✅ Claw-native, human-facing, hybrid | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+119 | **Why L2 exists** | ✅ L1 = trust layer, L2 = services layer | Whitepaper Ch3 |\n+120 \n+121 ---\n+122 \n  44 ## ✅ Decided — Mar 11, 2026 (Whitepaper Ch5 Restructure)\n  45 \n  46 | Question | Decision | Doc |\n  47 |----------|----------|-----|\n     ...","firstChangedLine":44},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773206097933}}
