{"type":"message","id":"c5c93528","parentId":"f4eb479c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T07:01:08.952Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54257dd0245cc4918d8c941bbaa\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 15:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54257dd0245cc4918d8c941bbaa]\n任亚伦: registration process seems fine, just that i think it need a website or domain, otherwise can't find it, right? ip address will change. also should add a signature for it's system?"}],"timestamp":1773212468934}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef676f21","parentId":"c5c93528","timestamp":"2026-03-11T07:01:27.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is giving feedback on the App Portal registration process:\n\n1. **Website/domain required** — Apps need a stable URL, can't use IP address (changes)\n2. **Signature for the system** — I think he means the app should sign something to prove it controls the key\n\nLet me respond to these points.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good points!\n\n**1. Website/Domain Required:**\n- Yes, apps need a stable address\n- IP addresses change, can't rely on them\n- Should require:\n  - Website URL (required for registration)\n  - Domain ownership verification (optional but recommended)\n\n**2. Signature for the system:**\n- You mean the app signs something to prove it controls the private key?\n- Like a \"proof of ownership\" challenge?\n- Example: App Portal sends a challenge, app signs it with its private key\n\n**Updated Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1: Generate Keys**\n- Developer generates Ed25519 key pair locally\n\n**Step 2: Submit Registration**\n- App name\n- Description\n- App type\n- **Website URL (required)**\n- Developer identity (optional)\n- Contact info\n- **Public key**\n\n**Step 3: Domain Verification (optional but recommended)**\n- App Portal verifies domain ownership\n- Like SSL certificate validation\n\n**Step 4: Key Verification**\n- App signs a challenge to prove key ownership\n\n**Step 5: Tier 0 Assignment**\n- Stored on L2, 30-day trial\n\nIs this what you meant by signature? Or something else?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773212468943}}
