{"type":"message","id":"8417c0d3","parentId":"2ac7f148","timestamp":"2026-03-11T07:24:16.236Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5425c72414b4c10989c4a58736a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 15:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5425c72414b4c10989c4a58736a]\n任亚伦: yes, domain and email is must. if has key, then use key to change all the info. if lost key and lost email. we can think about adding other recovery method, like the menmoric token, or google auth verify number or something later."}],"timestamp":1773213856219}}
{"type":"message","id":"e524592f","parentId":"8417c0d3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T07:24:33.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is confirming:\n1. Domain + email is required for Tier 1\n2. If has key → can change all info with key signature\n3. If lost key but has email → can recover\n4. If lost both key and email → need other recovery methods (future):\n   - Mnemonic token\n   - Google authenticator\n   - Other 2FA methods\n\nThis is about app recovery. Let me record this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good, multiple recovery layers:\n\n**Recovery Hierarchy:**\n1. **Has key** → Can change all info (sign with private key)\n2. **Lost key, has email** → Recover via email verification\n3. **Lost both** → Future recovery methods:\n   - Mnemonic token (like seed phrase)\n   - Google Authenticator (2FA)\n   - Other 2FA methods\n\n**This is similar to how entities handle recovery!**\n\nLet me add this to the docs:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3dcc387c959a40f9941b94c4","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"**Email Verification Purpose:**\n- Contact verification — prove contact is real\n- Key recovery — if developer loses private key\n- Notifications — important alerts about the app\n\n**Recovery Methods:**\n| Scenario | Recovery Method |\n|----------|-----------------|\n| Has key | Sign with private key to change all info |\n| Lost key, has email | Email verification to recover |\n| Lost both | Future: mnemonic token, Google Auth, 2FA |\n\n**Anti-Sybil Measures:**","oldText":"**Email Verification Purpose:**\n- Contact verification — prove contact is real\n- Key recovery — if developer loses private key\n- Notifications — important alerts about the app\n\n**Anti-Sybil Measures:**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773213856227}}
