{"type":"message","id":"6fe3f5fe","parentId":"0ef7e600","timestamp":"2026-03-11T07:38:29.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also update the L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md with the answers Allan provided.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Awaiting response on multiple owners question.\n\nLet me also update the docs with what we decided:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ad2170683dca4439a025442e","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"> Allan: \"domain and email is must. if has key, then use key to change all the info. if lost key and lost email, we can think about adding other recovery method, like the mnemonic token, or google auth verify number or something later.\" — Mar 11, 2026 15:24\n\n---\n\n### App Portal — Other Topics\n\n**App Updates:** Developer with key can update app profile anytime.\n\n**App Deprecation:** If app shuts down, record stays on L1 (permanent).\n\n**Ownership Transfer:** Developer can transfer key to new owner (we don't control).\n\n**Tier Demotion:** Governance rules for misbehaving apps (implementation detail).\n\n**Rate Limits:** Implementation detail, discuss later.\n\n**Multiple Owners:** Not supported natively — single key owner. Teams can use external multi-sig for shared control.\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"with key, just update app profile\" — Mar 11, 2026 15:30\n>\n> Allan: \"they can transfer key, we don't control\" — Mar 11, 2026 15:30","oldText":"> Allan: \"domain and email is must. if has key, then use key to change all the info. if lost key and lost email, we can think about adding other recovery method, like the mnemonic token, or google auth verify number or something later.\" — Mar 11, 2026 15:24"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalToken