{"type":"message","id":"88492625","parentId":"40b5e370","timestamp":"2026-03-11T08:55:09.473Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5426907bb490c3e485f63516aa5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 16:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5426907bb490c3e485f63516aa5]\n任亚伦: 5. need discuss 6. need put in chapter and discuss 7. implementation, need discuss 8, there are no private data on l1, if there are they are encrypted, it's decentralized, every node has copy 9. l1 data is public with some entryption fields. l2 data belongs to app, they are separated, not access across app unless permited.  10. l1 is public\nis this ok?"}],"timestamp":1773219309457}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b4df9d1","parentId":"88492625","timestamp":"2026-03-11T08:55:33.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is answering the questions I asked. Let me summarize:\n\n5. App lifecycle (governance for bad apps) - need discuss\n6. App economics - need put in chapter and discuss\n7. Monitoring - implementation, need discuss\n8. App permissions - L1 has no private data, or encrypted if there are. Decentralized, every node has copy.\n9. User consent - L1 data is public with some encrypted fields. L2 data belongs to app, separated, not access across app unless permitted.\n10. Data privacy - L1 is public\n\nThis clarifies a lot! Let me record this in the docs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Yes, this clarifies everything! Let me summarize:\n\n**5. App lifecycle:** Need discussion (governance for bad apps)\n\n**6. App economics:** Need chapter + discussion\n\n**7. Monitoring:** Implementation detail, discuss later\n\n**8. App permissions:** ✅ L1 has no private data. If there is, it's encrypted. Every node has copy (decentralized).\n\n**9. User consent:** ✅ \n- L1 data = public (some encrypted fields)\n- L2 data = belongs to app, separated, no cross-app access without permission\n\n**10. Data privacy:** ✅ L1 is public\n\nLet me record these in the docs:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_56a5d4da3c9642d7b29329d0","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"---\n\n## Operations Layer\n\n### App Lifecycle\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nGovernance rules for bad apps: rate limiting, flagging, delisting.\n\n### App Economics\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nFees, revenue sharing, incentives. Needs separate chapter.\n\n### Monitoring\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nUsage stats, health checks. Discuss during implementation.\n\n---\n\n## Security Layer\n\n### App Permissions\n\n**Function:** What data can apps access from L1?\n\n**Decision:** L1 has no private data. If private data exists, it's encrypted. Every node has full copy (decentralized).\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"there are no private data on l1, if there are they are encrypted, it's decentralized, every node has copy\" — Mar 11, 2026 16:55\n\n### User Consent\n\n**Function:** How users grant permission for data access?\n\n**Decision:** \n- L1 data = public (some encrypted fields)\n- L2 data = belongs to app, separated\n- No cross-app access without permission\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"l1 data is public with some encrypted fields. l2 data belongs to app, they are separated, not access across app unless permitted.\" — Mar 11, 2026 16:55\n\n### Data Privacy\n\n**Function:** What's private vs shared?\n\n**Decision:** L1 is public. L2 data controlled by each app.\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"l1 is public\" — Mar 11, 2026 16:55\n\n---","oldText":"---"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773219309463}}
