hared?\n+468 \n+469 **Decision:** L1 is public. L2 data controlled by each app.\n+470 \n+471 **Status:** ✅ Decided\n+472 \n+473 **Context & Discussion:**\n+474 > Allan: \"l1 is public\" — Mar 11, 2026 16:55\n+475 \n+476 ---\n+477 \n 416 ## Related Documents\n 417 \n 418 | Document | Date | Purpose |\n 419 |----------|------|---------|\n     ...","firstChangedLine":416},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773219410476}}
