{"type":"message","id":"91328e16","parentId":"74c68379","timestamp":"2026-03-11T08:57:38.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've recorded the Operations Layer and Security Layer decisions. Let me now check if there are any remaining topics to discuss.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Recorded in `L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md`:\n\n**Operations Layer:**\n- App Lifecycle → 🔴 Need discussion\n- App Economics → 🔴 Need discussion (separate chapter)\n- Monitoring → 🟡 Implementation detail\n\n**Security Layer:**\n- App Permissions → ✅ L1 no private data, encrypted if exists\n- User Consent → ✅ L1 public, L2 data separated\n- Data Privacy → ✅ L1 is public\n\nWhat's next? Remaining topics:\n- **Developer Layer** (SDK, testing, deployment)\n- **User Layer** (app management, data portability, accountability)\n- **Business/Ecosystem** (marketplace, incentives, governance)\n- **Technical Layer** (scaling, versioning, caching)\n- **Legal/Compliance** (ToS, ownership, audits)\n- **L1 Node Registration**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773219432802}}
