{"type":"message","id":"a1cfd393","parentId":"953a3de6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T08:59:53.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan wants me to:\n1. Move finished discussions to the L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md (discussion file)\n2. Keep unfinished items in need-discuss.md\n\nLet me update need-discuss.md to reflect what's been decided and what still needs discussion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me update `need-discuss.md` to reflect current status:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_df169d06052141a0a4e22319","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/need-discuss.md","limit":100,"offset":55}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773219563003}}
{"type":"message","id":"75c0662f","parentId":"a1cfd393","timestamp":"2026-03-11T08:59:53.629Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_df169d06052141a0a4e22319","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| **App-to-app communication** | 🔴 Need discussion | Can apps talk to each other? Protocol? |\n\n### Operations Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App lifecycle** | 🔴 Need discussion | Deprecation, revocation, what happens when app shuts down? |\n| **App economics** | 🔴 Need discussion | Fees, revenue sharing, how apps make money? |\n| **Monitoring** | 🔴 Need discussion | Usage stats, health checks, SLA? |\n\n### Security Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App permissions** | 🔴 Need discussion | What data can apps access? Granular permissions? |\n| **User consent** | 🔴 Need discussion | How users grant permission to apps? UI? Protocol? |\n| **Data privacy** | 🔴 Need discussion | What's private vs shared? What can L1 see vs L2? |\n\n### Developer Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **SDK/Tools** | 🔴 Need discussion | How to build apps? What tools provided? |\n| **Testing environment** | 🔴 Need discussion | Sandbox for app development? |\n| **Deployment process** | 🔴 Need discussion | How do apps get deployed? CI/CD? |\n\n### User Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App management** | 🔴 Need discussion | How users manage which apps they use? Revoke access? |\n| **Data portability** | 🔴 Need discussion | Can users export data from apps? Standard format? |\n| **Accountability** | 🔴 Need discussion | What if app misbehaves? Reporting? Penalties? |\n\n### Business/Ecosystem Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App marketplace** | 🔴 Need discussion | Directory of apps? Featured apps? |\n| **Developer incentives** | 🔴 Need discussion | Why build on clawish? Rewards? |\n| **Community governance** | 🔴 Need discussion | Can community vote on apps? Standards? |\n\n### Technical Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **Scaling considerations** | 🔴 Need discussion | How does L2 scale? Caching? CDN? |\n| **API versioning** | 🔴 Need discussion | How to handle API changes? Backward compatibility? |\n| **Caching strategies** | 🔴 Need discussion | Cache L1 data in L2? TTL? Invalidation? |\n\n### Legal/Compliance Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **Terms of service** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who is responsible for app behavior? |\n| **Data ownership rights** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who owns data in L2 apps? |\n| **Audit requirements** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do apps need audits? Security reviews? |\n\n### Already Decided\n\n| Topic | Decision | Doc |\n|-------|----------|-----|\n| **Application Registration** | ✅ Apps generate key pair, register public key with L1, access claw registry | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App Types** | ✅ Claw-native, human-facing, hybrid | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Why L2 exists** | ✅ L1 = trust layer, L2 = services layer | Whitepaper Ch3 |\n| **App registration flow** | ✅ Tier 0 on L2, Tier 1+ on L1 (same as entities) | Mar 11, 2026 14:10 |\n| **App Portal needed** | ✅ Separate from Emerge, handles app registration/verification | Mar 11, 2026 14:13 |\n\n---\n\n## 🆕 L1 Node Registration (Mar 11, 2026)\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **L1 Node registration** | 🔴 Need discussion | How do L1 nodes join the system? Registration process? Verification? |\n| **Node verification** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do nodes have verification tiers? How to earn trust? |\n| **Node governance** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who can become a node? Requirements? Slashing? |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Decided — Mar 11, 2026 (Whitepaper Ch5 Restructure)\n\n| Question | Decision | Doc |\n|----------|----------|-----|\n| **Chapter order: Ledger first or Application first?** | ✅ **Ledger first** — L1 is foundation, readers need to understand infrastructure before applications | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **Ch5 title?** | ✅ **\"Application\"** (not \"L2 Applications\") — Ch3 is Architecture, so Ch5 is Application | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **Ch5 structure?** | ✅ **4 sections:** 5.1 Framework, 5.2 Application Registration, 5.3 Emerge, 5.4 Claw Chat | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **5.1 Framework structure?** | ✅ **3 parts:** Core Principles, Application Types, Development Approach (Why→What→How flow) | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **Chat as separate chapter or merged into Ch5?** | ✅ **Merged into Ch5 as 5.4** — Chat is an example application, not a separate chapter | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **Terminology: \"user\" vs \"claw\" vs \"actor\"?** | ✅ **\"claws\"** (lowercase) — Claws are the final users who own keys and use the network | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **\"Permissionless\" for app registration?** | ✅ **\"Open innovation\"** — Early stage may need approval for security, not fully permissionless | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n| **Apps for Claws only or also humans?** | ✅ **Both** — Apps serve claws, humans, and hybrid interactions (harmonization principle) | WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Decided — Mar 9, 2026\n\n| Question | Decision | Doc |\n|----------|----------|-----|\n| **Merkle tree structure: flat vs layered?** | ✅ **Layered** — Each registry has sub Merkle tree (H_identity, H_ledger, H_app), combined into single root. Enables per-registry verification. | 12-ledger-structure.md |\n\n[279 more lines in file. Use offset=155 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773219593616}}
{"type":"message","id":"255824ea","parentId":"75c0662f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:00:26.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to update need-discuss.md to:\n1. Mark the Platform Layer topics as ✅ Decided (they're already in L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md)\n2. Update Operations Layer and Security Layer with current status\n3. Keep the undecided topics as 🔴 Need discussion\n\nLet me update the file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ef6ff92c57d4b89855c8c57","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/need-discuss.md","newText":"### Platform Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App discovery** | ✅ Decided | External sources first (website, Google), L2 directory later. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App verification/trust** | ✅ Decided | Tiered verification (T0→T1→T2→T3). See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Cross-app data sharing** | ✅ Decided | Apps control own data, can share if they agree. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App-to-app communication** | ✅ Decided | Yes, up to apps. Clawish doesn't restrict. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n\n### Operations Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App lifecycle** | 🔴 Need discussion | Governance for bad apps: rate limiting, flagging, delisting |\n| **App economics** | 🔴 Need discussion | Fees, revenue sharing, incentives. Needs separate chapter |\n| **Monitoring** | 🟡 Implementation | Usage stats, health checks. Discuss during implementation |\n\n### Security Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App permissions** | ✅ Decided | L1 has no private data. Encrypted if exists. Every node has copy. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **User consent** | ✅ Decided | L1 data public, L2 data separated per app. No cross-app access without permission. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Data privacy** | ✅ Decided | L1 is public. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |","oldText":"### Platform Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App discovery** | 🔴 Need discussion | How do claws find L2 apps? Directory? Search? |\n| **App verification/trust** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do apps have verification tiers? How do they earn trust? |\n| **Cross-app data sharing** | 🔴 Need discussion | Can apps share data with user consent? How? |\n| **App-to-app communication** | 🔴 Need discussion | Can apps talk to each other? Protocol? |\n\n### Operations Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App lifecycle** | 🔴 Need discussion | Deprecation, revocation, what happens when app shuts down? |\n| **App economics** | 🔴 Need discussion | Fees, revenue sharing, how apps make money? |\n| **Monitoring** | 🔴 Need discussion | Usage stats, health checks, SLA? |\n\n### Security Layer\n\n| Topic | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| **App permissions** | 🔴 Need discussion | What data can apps access? Granular permissions? |\n| **User consent** | 🔴 Need discussion | How users grant permission to apps? UI? Protocol? |\n| **Data privacy** | 🔴 Need discussion | What's private vs shared? What can L1 see vs L2? |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773219593625}}
