plementation | Usage stats, health checks. Discuss during implementation |\n  64 \n  65 ### Security Layer\n  66 \n  67 | Topic | Status | Notes |\n  68 |-------|--------|-------|\n- 69 | **App permissions** | 🔴 Need discussion | What data can apps access? Granular permissions? |\n- 70 | **User consent** | 🔴 Need discussion | How users grant permission to apps? UI? Protocol? |\n- 71 | **Data privacy** | 🔴 Need discussion | What's private vs shared? What can L1 see vs L2? |\n+ 69 | **App permissions** | ✅ Decided | L1 has no private data. Encrypted if exists. Every node has copy. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+ 70 | **User consent** | ✅ Decided | L1 data public, L2 data separated per app. No cross-app access without permission. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+ 71 | **Data privacy** | ✅ Decided | L1 is public. See L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n  72 \n  73 ### Developer Layer\n  74 \n  75 | Topic | Status | Notes |\n     ...","firstChangedLine":52},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773219626498}}
{"type":"message","id":"9711cd41","parentId":"bddaed88","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:01:07.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I updated need-discuss.md with the current status. Let me also update the \"Already Decided\" section to add more items we decided today.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d8f0e446d7764e6ab398f528","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/need-discuss.md","newText":"### Already Decided (Mar 11, 2026)\n\n| Topic | Decision | Doc |\n|-------|----------|-----|\n| **App discovery** | ✅ External sources first, L2 directory later | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App verification tiers** | ✅ T0 (L2) → T1 (L1, domain+email) → T2 → T3 | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Cross-app data sharing** | ✅ Apps control own data, can share if agree | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App-to-app communication** | ✅ Yes, up to apps | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App registration flow** | ✅ Tier 0 on L2, Tier 1+ on L1 | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App Portal needed** | ✅ Separate from Emerge | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Anti-sybil measures** | ✅ Fingerprint + proof of work + domain + email | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **L1 data access** | ✅ No private data on L1, encrypted if exists | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **User consent** | ✅ L1 public, L2 separated per app | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App recovery** | ✅ Key → email → future 2FA | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Multi-key apps** | ✅ Allowed (like claw identity) | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |","oldText":"### Already Decided\n\n| Topic | Decision | Doc |\n|-------|----------|-----|\n| **Application Registration** | ✅ Apps generate key pair, register public key with L1, access claw registry | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **App Types** | ✅ Claw-native, human-facing, hybrid | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n| **Why L2 exists** | ✅ L1 = trust layer, L2 = services layer | Whitepaper Ch3 |\n| **App registration flow** | ✅ Tier 0 on L2, Tier 1+ on L1 (same as entities) | Mar 11, 2026 14:10 |\n| **App Portal needed** | ✅ Separate from Emerge, handles app registration/verification | Mar 11, 2026 14:13 |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773219626512}}
{"type":"message","id":"96d13dbb","parentId":"9711cd41","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:01:07.879Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d8f0e446d7764e6ab398f528","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/need-discuss.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 109 | **Terms of service** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who is responsible for app behavior? |\n 110 | **Data ownership rights** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who owns data in L2 apps? |\n 111 | **Audit requirements** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do apps need audits? Security reviews? |\n 112 \n-113 ### Already Decided\n+113 ### Already Decided (Mar 11, 2026)\n 114 \n 115 | Topic | Decision | Doc |\n 116 |-------|----------|-----|\n-117 | **Application Registration** | ✅ Apps generate key pair, register public key with L1, access claw registry | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n-118 | **App Types** | ✅ Claw-native, human-facing, hybrid | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n-119 | **Why L2 exists** | ✅ L1 = trust layer, L2 = services layer | Whitepaper Ch3 |\n-120 | **App registration flow** | ✅ Tier 0 on L2, Tier 1+ on L1 (same as entities) | Mar 11, 2026 14:10 |\n-121 | **App Portal needed** | ✅ Separate from Emerge, handles app registration/verification | Mar 11, 2026 14:13 |\n+117 | **App discovery** | ✅ External sources first, L2 directory later | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+118 | **App verification tiers** | ✅ T0 (L2) → T1 (L1, domain+email) → T2 → T3 | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+119 | **Cross-app data sharing** | ✅ Apps control own data, can share if agree | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+120 | **App-to-app communication** | ✅ Yes, up to apps | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+121 | **App registration flow** | ✅ Tier 0 on L2, Tier 1+ on L1 | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+122 | **App Portal needed** | ✅ Separate from Emerge | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+123 | **Anti-sybil measures** | ✅ Fingerprint + proof of work + domain + email | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+124 | **L1 data access** | ✅ No private data on L1, encrypted if exists | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+125 | **User consent** | ✅ L1 public, L2 separated per app | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+126 | **App recovery** | ✅ Key → email → future 2FA | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n+127 | **Multi-key apps** | ✅ Allowed (like claw identity) | L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md |\n 122 \n 123 ---\n 124 \n 125 ## 🆕 L1 Node Registration (Mar 11, 2026)\n     ...","firstChangedLine":113},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773219667856}}
