{"type":"message","id":"56bd2986","parentId":"976b31af","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:02:19.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I've updated:\n1. L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md with all the Platform Layer, Operations Layer, and Security Layer decisions\n2. need-discuss.md with current status:\n   - Platform Layer: all ✅ Decided\n   - Operations Layer: lifecycle/economics 🔴 need discussion, monitoring 🟡 implementation\n   - Security Layer: all ✅ Decided\n   - Added \"Already Decided\" section with all decisions from today\n\nNow waiting for Allan's guidance on what to discuss next.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Updated `need-discuss.md`:\n\n**✅ Decided (recorded in L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md):**\n- Platform Layer: discovery, verification, cross-app data, app-to-app\n- Security Layer: permissions, consent, privacy\n- Registration: flow, anti-sybil, recovery, multi-key\n\n**🔴 Still need discussion:**\n- Operations Layer: lifecycle (governance for bad apps), economics (separate chapter)\n- Developer Layer: SDK, testing, deployment\n- User Layer: app management, data portability, accountability\n- Business/Ecosystem: marketplace, incentives, governance\n- Technical: scaling, versioning, caching\n- Legal: ToS, ownership, audits\n- L1 Node Registration\n\nWhat should we discuss next?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773219698163}}
