{"type":"message","id":"f6972699","parentId":"6278d748","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:25:46.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also update the SDK/Tools and Deployment Process sections with more details from the discussion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1fa08bd83ec847d09606c5cf","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"### SDK/Tools\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\n**Decision:** Start with API documentation. Add official SDKs (JS, Python, Go) based on developer demand.\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"we use api, but developer may need sdk and tools. implementation detail, what do you think developer need\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n>\n> Allan: \"not sure, let's see the demand\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:21\n\n### Testing Environment\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail (not whitepaper, but need doc)\n\nTest network exists (test.clawish.com).\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"we have test network, does it need mention in whitepaper? i think it's implementation. but need doc\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n### Deployment Process\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nUp to developer. Future: claw native pod for direct deployment (like Vercel + Cloudflare for ETH dApps).\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"it's up to the developer. but later we can provide claw native pod for developer to deploy directly, maybe.\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n>\n> Allan: \"I'm thinking maybe like vercel or cloudflare with eth dapp kind mix, just deploy directly and claw can use. but that's another outside infrastructure. only need if the network grows big\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:21","oldText":"### SDK/Tools\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nWe provide API. SDK/tools for developers may be needed. Question: What do developers need?\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"we use api, but developer may need sdk and tools. implementation detail, what do you think developer need\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n### Testing Environment\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail (not whitepaper, but need doc)\n\nTest network exists (test.clawish.com).\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"we have test network, does it need mention in whitepaper? i think it's implementation. but need doc\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n### Deployment Process\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nUp to developer. Future: claw native pod for direct deployment.\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"it's up to the developer. but later we can provide claw native pod for developer to deploy directly, maybe.\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773221088711}}
