{"type":"message","id":"83963ff2","parentId":"3355c3eb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:33:16.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me find a unique place to add this section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ad8a3eed730541fe839f0f05","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","limit":20,"offset":540}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773221575448}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0519fe4","parentId":"83963ff2","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:33:16.238Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad8a3eed730541fe839f0f05","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n**Decision:** L2 data determined by L2 app (not us). L1 data is open/public.\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"l2 is determine by l2 app, not us. l1 is open\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n### Accountability\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nGovernance issue: report mechanism, deduct merits, demote app tier.\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"governance issue, may report or something, deduct app merits? demote app? implementation detail\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n---\n\n## Related Documents\n\n[24 more lines in file. Use offset=560 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773221596212}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ac4e9f5","parentId":"c0519fe4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:33:55.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can add the new sections after \"Accountability\" and before \"Related Documents\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_df5574f8138a4749b8187127","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"governance issue, may report or something, deduct app merits? demote app? implementation detail\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n---\n\n## Business/Ecosystem Layer\n\n### App Marketplace\n\n**Function:** Official app directory for discovering L2 apps.\n\n**Decision:** Yes, build official app store for clawish. Like App Store / Play Store but for L2 apps.\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Rationale:**\n- Official source of trusted apps\n- Discoverable by claws\n- clawish controls quality (verified apps featured)\n- If we don't build it, someone else will\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"it's nice to have a native directory, if we don't do, some one will build it. it's like app store, i think we need to do it as offical market.\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:32\n\n### Developer Incentives\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nSeparate incentive chapter needed. Why build on clawish? Fun, make money, gain exposure, show skills, love claws?\n\n### Community Governance\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nCan community vote on app tier promotion/demotion? App governance through voting?\n\n---\n\n## Technical Layer\n\n### Scaling\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nCaching, CDN strategies.\n\n### API Versioning\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nBackward compatibility handling.\n\n### Caching Strategies\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nTTL, invalidation patterns.\n\n---\n\n## Legal/Compliance Layer\n\n### Terms of Service\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nWho is responsible for app behavior? What do other blockchains say?\n\n### Data Ownership\n\n**Decision:** Who has the key owns the data.\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"who has the key who owns, right?\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:29\n\n### Audit Requirements\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail\n\nSecurity reviews for higher tiers (Tier 2, 3).\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"yes, need for developement\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:29\n\n---\n\n## Related Documents","oldText":"**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"governance issue, may report or something, deduct app merits? demote app? implementation detail\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:07\n\n---\n\n## Related Documents"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773221596231}}
