{"type":"message","id":"9861dc20","parentId":"b45897f3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:40:19.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good clarifications from Allan:\n\n19. Community governance - needs discussion. Community = everyone in ecosystem (developers, node runners, app builders, users). This is about the whole ecosystem governance. Should it be in whitepaper?\n\n23. ToS - needs a waiver (implementation detail)\n\n25. Audit - if network grows, can have audit anytime needed.\n\nLet me record these.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it!\n\n**19. Community governance:**\n- Community = everyone in ecosystem (developers, node runners, app builders, users)\n- Whole ecosystem governance question\n- Should we mention in whitepaper?\n\n**23. ToS:**\n- Write a waiver\n- Implementation detail\n\n**25. Audit:**\n- If network grows, audits can be done anytime\n- Implementation detail"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5362c370c90d44ada9d30d47","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"### Community Governance\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\n**Question:** Should ecosystem governance be mentioned in whitepaper?\n\n**Context:** Community = everyone in ecosystem (developers, node runners, app builders, users). Whole ecosystem governance, not just app governance.\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"may include developer, node runner and app builder, everyone in the ecosystem is community? yes, this is a whole eco system, do we need mention in paper?\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:39","oldText":"### Community Governance\n\n**Status:** 🔴 Need discussion\n\nCan community vote on app tier promotion/demotion? App governance through voting?"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"c