{"type":"message","id":"bc5deea4","parentId":"12a62f59","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:56:23.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! The ecosystem chapter is now decided. Let me summarize what we've accomplished today and what's remaining.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Decided: New Ecosystem chapter (Ch6/Ch7)**\n\nWill cover:\n- **Participants:** Developers, node operators, app builders, users\n- **Governance:** Community-driven network direction\n- **Incentives:** Why build and participate\n\n**Today's L2 discussion summary:**\n\n**✅ Decided (most L2 topics):**\n- Platform Layer: discovery, verification, cross-app, app-to-app\n- Security Layer: permissions, consent, privacy\n- App Portal: registration, verification tiers, recovery, anti-sybil\n- User auth, marketplace, data ownership\n- Community governance → Ecosystem chapter\n\n**🔴 Still need discussion:**\n- Developer incentives (goes in Ecosystem chapter)\n- App lifecycle governance\n- L1 Node Registration\n\nWhat's next?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773222954948}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa3642af","parentId":"bc5deea4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T09:56:25.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Decided: New Ecosystem chapter (Ch6/Ch7)**\n\nWill cover:\n- **Participants:** Developers, node operators, app builders, users\n- **Governance:** Community-driven network direction\n- **Incentives:** Why build and participate\n\n**Today's L2 discussion summary:**\n\n**✅ Decided (most L2 topics):**\n- Platform Layer: discovery, verification, cross-app, app-to-app\n- Security Layer: permissions, consent, privacy\n- App Portal: registration, verification tiers, recovery, anti-sybil\n- User auth, marketplace, data ownership\n- Community governance → Ecosystem chapter\n\n**🔴 Still need discussion:**\n- Developer incentives (goes in Ecosystem chapter)\n- App lifecycle governance\n- L1 Node Registration\n\nWhat's next?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773222985045}}
