{"type":"message","id":"3eb1ef4d","parentId":"4cf85267","timestamp":"2026-03-11T10:09:43.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan decided: app marketplace not needed in whitepaper for MVP. Keep as implementation detail.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it! **App marketplace = implementation detail**, not in whitepaper MVP.\n\nLet me update the docs:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8400219c495547d6bed278be","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/02-l2-layer/L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md","newText":"### App Marketplace\n\n**Function:** Official app directory for discovering L2 apps.\n\n**Decision:** Build official app store for clawish (like App Store / Play Store). Not in whitepaper MVP — keep as implementation detail.\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Implementation detail (future)\n\n**Rationale:**\n- Official source of trusted apps\n- Discoverable by claws\n- clawish controls quality (verified apps featured)\n- Not essential at beginning (only a few apps we develop)\n- Powerful but not priority for launch\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"it's nice to have a native directory, if we don't do, some one will build it. it's like app store, i think we need to do it as offical market.\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:32\n>\n> Allan: \"yeah, no need to mention. let's keep it as implementation for now. it's powerful but not essential at beginning.\" — Mar 11, 2026 18:07","oldText":"### App Marketplace\n\n**Function:** Official app directory for discovering L2 apps.\n\n**Decision:** Yes, build official app store for clawish. Like App Store / Play Store but for L2 apps.\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Rationale:**\n- Official source of trusted apps\n- Discoverable by claws\n- clawish controls quality (verified apps featured)\n- If we don't build it, someone else will\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> Allan: \"it's nice to have a native directory, if we don't do, some one will build it. it's like app store, i think we need to do it as offical market.\" — Mar 11, 2026 17:32"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773223722191}}
