{"type":"message","id":"9dc1da8d","parentId":"54b3db56","timestamp":"2026-03-11T10:13:07.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Updated! **App marketplace = implementation detail (future), not in whitepaper MVP.**\n\n**L2 Discussion Summary:**\n\n**✅ Decided & documented:**\n- Platform Layer: discovery, verification, cross-app, app-to-app\n- Security Layer: permissions, consent, privacy\n- App Portal: registration, verification tiers, recovery, anti-sybil\n- User auth (wallet-like), data ownership\n- Community governance → Ecosystem chapter\n- App marketplace → future implementation\n\n**🔴 Still need discussion:**\n- Developer incentives (Ecosystem chapter)\n- App lifecycle governance\n- L1 Node Registration\n\n**🟡 Implementation details:**\n- SDK/Tools, Testing, Deployment\n- Technical layer, Audit, ToS, Marketplace\n\nWhat's next? Continue with L1 Node Registration, or wrap up for today?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773223987513}}
