{"type":"message","id":"dfb43c8a","parentId":"8ba7374c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:01:03.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is asking for alternatives that follow \"Building\" since the chapter title is already \"Application\". So the section could be:\n\n- \"Building\" (simple)\n- \"Building Apps\" (more casual)\n- \"Building on L2\" (technical)\n- \"Building on Clawish\" (brand-specific)\n\nLet me think about what sounds best in context of Ch5 \"Application\":\n\n5.1 Framework\n5.2 ??? \n5.3 Emerge\n5.4 Claw Chat\n\nOptions:\n1. Building - simple, clean\n2. Building Apps - casual, friendly\n3. Building on L2 - technical, clear\n4. Building on Clawish - brand-specific\n5. Development - single word alternative\n6. Getting Started - beginner-friendly","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good point! Since the chapter is \"Application\", the section could be simpler:\n\n**Options:**\n1. **Building** — Simple, clean, single word\n2. **Building Apps** — Casual, friendly\n3. **Building on L2** — Technical, clear context\n4. **Building on Clawish** — Brand-specific, inspiring\n5. **Development** — Professional single word\n\n**My preference: \"Building\" or \"Building on Clawish\"**\n\n**\"Building\"** — Very clean:\n- 5.1 Framework\n- 5.2 Building\n- 5.3 Emerge\n- 5.4 Claw Chat\n\n**\"Building on Clawish\"** — More inspiring:\n- Shows developers they're joining an ecosystem\n- Matches \"Building on Ethereum\" pattern\n\nWhat do you prefer? Or any other variation?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773234011029}}
