{"type":"message","id":"f1d6ac47","parentId":"28a2a0cf","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:14:14.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking for more conceptual name options for section 5.2. Let me think of conceptual, high-level names that would work well for a whitepaper section about building applications on clawish.\n\nCurrent context:\n- 5.1 Framework (principles, types, development approach)\n- 5.2 [TBD] - Registration, verification, connection, auth for developers\n- 5.3 Emerge (entity registration app)\n- 5.4 Claw Chat (messaging app)\n\nThe name should be:\n- Conceptual (not too detailed/technical)\n- Professional\n- Fit between Framework and specific apps\n- Cover: registration, verification, connection, authentication\n\nLet me brainstorm more conceptual names:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Conceptual names for 5.2:**\n\n**Foundation/Structure:**\n1. **Building Foundation** — Solid base for building\n2. **Core Concepts** — Essential knowledge\n3. **Foundational Elements** — Building blocks\n4. **Structural Overview** — How it's organized\n\n**Entry/Beginning:**\n5. **Getting Started** — Friendly, beginner-focused\n6. **Building Introduction** — Intro before details\n7. **Entry Point** — Where to start\n8. **First Steps** — Beginning the journey\n\n**Knowledge/Understanding:**\n9. **Essential Knowledge** — What you need to know\n10. **Key Concepts** — Important ideas\n11. **Understanding L2** — Conceptual framing\n12. **The Basics** — Simple, clear\n\n**Process/Flow:**\n13. **The Building Process** — How building works\n14. **Development Flow** — Natural progression\n15. **Building Pathway** — Journey from idea to app\n\n**My top 3:**\n1. **Building Foundation** — Strong, authoritative\n2. **Essential Knowledge** — Clear purpose\n3. **Core Concepts** — Simple, conceptual\n\nWhat resonates with you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"i