{"type":"message","id":"5899896d","parentId":"17789504","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:53:43.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is asking about renaming the third section of 5.1 from \"Development Approach\" to something else since 5.2 is now called \"Development\". \n\nHe suggested options and I proposed \"Layer Separation\" or \"Layer Purpose\".\n\nLet me wait for his response. But first let me update the daily memory with this discussion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ab83f2e12894c49ad57f478","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md","newText":"- 21:45 PM — Final Ch5 structure: 5.1 Framework, 5.2 Development, 5.3 User Access, 5.4 Emerge, 5.5 Claw Chat. Updated need-discuss.md\n- 21:51 PM — Allan: 5.1 item 3 should rename (avoid confusion with 5.2 Development). Options: Layer Separation, Layer Purpose, Layer Roles?\n- 21:52 PM — Heartbeat: discussing rename of 5.1 third section with Allan","oldText":"- 21:45 PM — Final Ch5 structure: 5.1 Framework, 5.2 Development, 5.3 User Access, 5.4 Emerge, 5.5 Claw Chat. Updated need-discuss.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773237149130}}
