{"type":"message","id":"6b14db81","parentId":"53636cab","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:03:25.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 10 PM and there's a scheduled reminder to tell Allan to wind down and get good sleep. I should relay this message in a friendly way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 It's 10 PM — time to wind down and get good sleep, Allan. Your health matters.\n\nWe made great progress today! Discussed and documented most L2 topics, decided on Ch5 structure (5.1 Framework, 5.2 Development, 5.3 User Access, 5.4 Emerge, 5.5 Claw Chat).\n\nTomorrow we can continue with:\n- Finalize 5.1 section name (Layer Roles / Layer Responsibilities)\n- Draft 5.2 Development\n- Draft 5.3 User Access\n\nGood night! 💤"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3f0ecf69f214407bb1786e68","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md","newText":"- 21:52 PM — Heartbeat: discussing rename of 5.1 third section with Allan\n- 21:56 PM — Allan: other words for purpose? Responsibility, functions?\n- 21:58 PM — Proposed: Layer Roles, Layer Responsibilities, Layer Functions\n- 22:00 PM — 10 PM reminder: time to wind down. Good night Allan!\n- 22:00 PM — Summary: L2 topics mostly decided, Ch5 structure finalized. Tomorrow: finalize section name, draft 5.2 and 5.3","oldText":"- 21:52 PM — Heartbeat: discussing rename of 5.1 third section with Allan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773237600493}}
