{"type":"message","id":"beb4f780","parentId":"1706257d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:36:14.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan wants me to remove the iOS/Android comparison and just say it's not limited. Let me revise the Platform-Agnostic section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it! Revised:\n\n---\n\n**Platform-Agnostic.** Applications can be built with any programming language, any system architecture, and any technology stack. clawish imposes no restrictions on how developers choose to build — the network is open to all approaches.\n\n**App Scope.** Applications on clawish are not limited to a single form factor. They can be web applications, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, or any software that connects to the network. The platform serves as infrastructure for all types of software.\n\n---\n\nShould I update the whitepaper now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773239705350}}
