{"type":"message","id":"0e3ad507","parentId":"6d8a67f1","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:48:29.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's getting late (10:46 PM). Allan is still engaged and wants to finish. I proposed renaming:\n- \"Platform-Agnostic\" → \"Language-Agnostic\" \n- \"App Scope\" → \"Multi-Platform\"\n\nLet me wait for Allan's confirmation on these names.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Proposed final naming:\n- **Language-Agnostic** — Any programming language/technology\n- **Multi-Platform** — Runs across web, CLI, mobile, backend\n\nAwaiting your confirmation. It's late — we can also continue tomorrow! 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773240429803}}
{"type":"message","id":"06e0d36b","parentId":"0e3ad507","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:48:29.508Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542c497170b0c2cc5d625d17baa\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 22:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542c497170b0c2cc5d625d17baa]\n任亚伦: mobile can be mobile apps, and last line should it be  ....all of these platforms? do we need add any os system as well in the multiplatform?"}],"timestamp":1773240509485}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c1147e4","parentId":"06e0d36b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:49:56.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is suggesting:\n1. \"mobile clients\" → \"mobile apps\"\n2. Last line should say \"all of these platforms\" instead of \"any or all of these interfaces\"\n3. Question: should we add OS systems (Windows, Linux, macOS) to multi-platform?\n\nLet me think about this - we're talking about:\n- Language-Agnostic: any programming language\n- Multi-Platform: web, CLI, mobile apps, backend services\n\nShould we include OS? I think \"backend services\" could cover server-side which runs on any OS. But explicitly mentioning OS systems might be clearer.\n\nLet me propose an updated version.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good points!\n\n**Updated Multi-Platform:**\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications run across multiple platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, and desktop applications. The same application can serve users across all of these platforms.\n\nOr include OS explicitly:\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications run across multiple platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, desktop applications on Windows, macOS, and Linux, and backend services. The same application can serve users across all of these platforms.\n\nWhich version do you prefer? Include OS or keep it simpler?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773240509497}}
{"type":"message","id":"01dffa3a","parentId":"4c1147e4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:49:56.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good points!\n\n**Updated Multi-Platform:**\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications run across multiple platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, and desktop applications. The same application can serve users across all of these platforms.\n\nOr include OS explicitly:\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications run across multiple platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, desktop applications on Windows, macOS, and Linux, and backend services. The same application can serve users across all of these platforms.\n\nWhich version do you prefer? Include OS or keep it simpler?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773240596987}}
{"type":"message","id":"502d4fb0","parentId":"01dffa3a","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:52:08.167Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542c57ae40a0c2900c32a657b60\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 22:52 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542c57ae40a0c2900c32a657b60]\n任亚伦: no need specify system. and it's not applications run across, sound like one program can run all platform. it's applications can be design or develop from or for or across different platforms? what's the wording do you think fit?"}],"timestamp":1773240728148}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e0bb36a","parentId":"502d4fb0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:53:30.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is right. The current wording \"applications run across multiple platforms\" sounds like one app runs everywhere (like a cross-platform app).\n\nBut the meaning should be: developers can CHOOSE to build for any platform. Not that one app automatically runs everywhere.\n\nBetter wording:\n- \"Applications can be developed for different platforms...\"\n- \"Applications can be designed for any platform...\"\n- \"Developers can build for multiple platforms...\"\n\nLet me suggest better wording that captures the freedom to choose, not automatic cross-platform capability.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"You're right! The current wording sounds like automatic cross-platform.\n\n**Better options:**\n\n**Option 1:**\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications can be developed for different platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, and desktop applications. Developers choose the platforms that suit their needs.\n\n**Option 2:**\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications can be designed for any platform — web, CLI, mobile, backend, or desktop. The network supports all platforms without restrictions.\n\n**Option 3:**\n**Multi-Platform.** Developers can build applications for multiple platforms: web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, and desktop applications. clawish imposes no platform restrictions.\n\nWhich wording captures it best? You choose the platform, not one app running everywhere."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773240728158}}
{"type":"message","id":"48d9efc3","parentId":"7e0bb36a","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:56:25.331Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542c674b6ca4c29479e00ae2790\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 22:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542c674b6ca4c29479e00ae2790]\n任亚伦: option 2 sounds good. just a little bit short"}],"timestamp":1773240985302}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ccfea2c","parentId":"48d9efc3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:57:56.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User likes option 2 but wants it slightly longer/more detailed. Let me expand it a bit while keeping the same structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Expanded Option 2:**\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications can be designed for any platform — web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, or desktop applications. The network supports all platforms without restrictions, allowing developers to reach users wherever they are.\n\nOr even more detail:\n\n**Multi-Platform.** Applications can be designed for any platform — web interfaces, command-line tools, mobile apps, backend services, or desktop applications. clawish provides the same identity and network access across all platforms, giving developers complete freedom in choosing how to reach their users.\n\nWhich version works better?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773240985319}}
