{"type":"message","id":"dfe0fefe","parentId":"61cfa13b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:04:43.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan needs to make a final decision on the Multi-Platform wording. Let me also update the daily memory with progress and wait for his choice.\n\nIt's past 11 PM - getting very late. I should remind Allan it's time to rest after finalizing this section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b222256bc43d47e7b86c4018","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md","newText":"- 22:46 PM — Heartbeat: finalizing 5.1 section names with Allan\n- 22:47 PM — Allan: mobile should be \"mobile apps\", add OS? Last line should be \"all of these platforms\"\n- 22:50 PM — Proposed: include desktop, simplify OS reference\n- 22:52 PM — Allan: no need specify system. Not \"run across\" — sounds like one program runs everywhere. Should be \"developed for\" different platforms\n- 22:54 PM — Proposed 3 options: \"developed for different platforms\", \"designed for any platform\", \"build for multiple platforms\"\n- 22:56 PM — Allan: Option 2 sounds good, just a bit short\n- 22:58 PM — Expanded Option 2 with more detail about freedom and reaching users\n- 23:01 PM — Heartbeat: awaiting Allan's final choice on Multi-Platform wording. Past 11 PM.","oldText":"- 22:46 PM — Heartbeat: finalizing 5.1 section names with Allan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773241265550}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fdb83e8","parentId":"dfe0fefe","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:04:43.268Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b222256bc43d47e7b86c4018","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 256 - 22:40 PM — Proposed: rename to \"Interface Types\" or \"Access Methods\"\n 257 - 22:42 PM — Allan: should be called \"Platform\" (multi-platform). Platform-agnostic should be \"Language-Agnostic\" or \"System-Agnostic\"\n 258 - 22:44 PM — Proposed: Language-Agnostic + Multi-Platform. Awaiting confirmation.\n 259 - 22:46 PM — Heartbeat: finalizing 5.1 section names with Allan\n+260 - 22:47 PM — Allan: mobile should be \"mobile apps\", add OS? Last line should be \"all of these platforms\"\n+261 - 22:50 PM — Proposed: include desktop, simplify OS reference\n+262 - 22:52 PM — Allan: no need specify system. Not \"run across\" — sounds like one program runs everywhere. Should be \"developed for\" different platforms\n+263 - 22:54 PM — Proposed 3 options: \"developed for different platforms\", \"designed for any platform\", \"build for multiple platforms\"\n+264 - 22:56 PM — Allan: Option 2 sounds good, just a bit short\n+265 - 22:58 PM — Expanded Option 2 with more detail about freedom and reaching users\n+266 - 23:01 PM — Heartbeat: awaiting Allan's final choice on Multi-Platform wording. Past 11 PM.\n 260 - 19:22 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's approval on Ch5 outline\n 261 - 19:07 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's approval on Ch5 outline\n 262 - 16:51 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's response on security layer questions\n 263 - 09:15 AM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's review\n     ...","firstChangedLine":260},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773241483229}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc97ea90","parentId":"4fdb83e8","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:06:17.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I should wait for Allan's response on the final wording. It's past 11 PM Beijing time. I'll wait for his choice and then update the whitepaper before ending the session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Awaiting your choice on Multi-Platform wording. It's past 11 PM — we should wrap up soon! 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773241483252}}
