{"type":"message","id":"d55167d1","parentId":"ae36695e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:30:09.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan wants to see the outline for 5.2 Development and 5.3 User Access before we wrap up for the night. Let me summarize the outlines based on our earlier discussion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**5.2 Development** (developer perspective):\n\n- **Overview** — What this section covers\n- **Registration** — Generate keys, register with App Portal (L2), Tier 0\n- **Verification** — Tier progression (T0→T1→T2→T3), domain + email verification, promotion to L1\n- **Connection to L1** — Access claw registry (public identity data)\n\n**5.3 User Access** (user perspective):\n\n- **Overview** — What this section covers\n- **Discovery** — How users find apps (external sources first, L2 directory later)\n- **Authentication** — Wallet-like login using L1 identity\n- **Data Access** — L1 data is public, L2 data is app-controlled\n\n---\n\nShould I draft these tomorrow with this outline? Good night! 🦞💤"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1e25bfa3a172477d85dac9e9","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md","newText":"- 23:21 PM — Session complete. 5.1 Framework finalized. Tomorrow: draft 5.2 Development and 5.3 User Access.\n- 23:29 PM — Allan: show me 5.2 and 5.3 outline first\n- 23:30 PM — Showed outlines: 5.2 (Overview, Registration, Verification, Connection) and 5.3 (Overview, Discovery, Authentication, Data Access)","oldText":"- 23:21 PM — Session complete. 5.1 Framework finalized. Tomorrow: draft 5.2 Development and 5.3 User Access."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773242940663}}
