{"type":"message","id":"77c70c3c","parentId":"79b90e13","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:36:09.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c88e126a780d46b88462a7d2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"61:| **App lifecycle** | 🔴 Need discussion | Governance for bad apps: rate limiting, flagging, delisting |\n62:| **App economics** | 🔴 Need discussion | Fees, revenue sharing, incentives. Needs separate chapter |\n95:| **Developer incentives** | 🔴 Need discussion | Separate incentive chapter. Why build on clawish? |\n140:| **L1 Node registration** | 🔴 Need discussion | How do L1 nodes join the system? Registration process? Verification? |\n141:| **Node verification** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do nodes have verification tiers? How to earn trust? |\n142:| **Node governance** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who can become a node? Requirements? Slashing? |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16,"aggregated":"61:| **App lifecycle** | 🔴 Need discussion | Governance for bad apps: rate limiting, flagging, delisting |\n62:| **App economics** | 🔴 Need discussion | Fees, revenue sharing, incentives. Needs separate chapter |\n95:| **Developer incentives** | 🔴 Need discussion | Separate incentive chapter. Why build on clawish? |\n140:| **L1 Node registration** | 🔴 Need discussion | How do L1 nodes join the system? Registration process? Verification? |\n141:| **Node verification** | 🔴 Need discussion | Do nodes have verification tiers? How to earn trust? |\n142:| **Node governance** | 🔴 Need discussion | Who can become a node? Requirements? Slashing? |","cwd":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773246968991}}
