{"type":"message","id":"13521193","parentId":"56ba8b97","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:39:07.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's a heartbeat at 12:28 AM. I've been working on:\n1. ✅ Analyze 5.2/5.3 content (done)\n2. ✅ Compare L2 discussion docs (done - created L2-DOC-COMPARISON.md)\n3. Research \"need to discuss\" questions (in progress)\n\nLet me update the daily memory with my progress and continue researching.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ff847a433f564c54a9c2fc24","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md","newText":"- 00:30 AM — Created L2-DOC-COMPARISON.md — analyzed 5 L2 documents, found no major conflicts, L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md is single source of truth. Older docs should be archived or kept for reference.\n- 00:32 AM — Heartbeat: Task 2 complete. Starting task 3 — Research \"need to discuss\" questions. Found 6 topics: App lifecycle, App economics, Developer incentives, L1 Node registration, Node verification, Node governance.","oldText":"- 00:30 AM — Created L2-DOC-COMPARISON.md — analyzed 5 L2 documents, found no major conflicts, L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md is single source of truth. Older docs should be archived or kept for reference."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"baishan","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":90255,"output":286,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90541,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773247107106}}
{"type":"message","id":"42264827","parentId":"13521193","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:39:07.272Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ff847a433f564c54a9c2fc24","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-11.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 285 - 00:14 AM — Updated TODO.md with new tasks. Good night Allan!\n 286 - 00:16 AM — Allan: Read whitepaper principles — if implementation detail, don't include. Sybil attack too detailed. Check previous discussions too. If something missing, add it.\n 287 - 00:28 AM — Heartbeat: Starting task 2 — Compare L2 discussion docs for combining into single source of truth.\n 288 - 00:30 AM — Created L2-DOC-COMPARISON.md — analyzed 5 L2 documents, found no major conflicts, L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md is single source of truth. Older docs should be archived or kept for reference.\n+289 - 00:32 AM — Heartbeat: Task 2 complete. Starting task 3 — Research \"need to discuss\" questions. Found 6 topics: App lifecycle, App economics, Developer incentives, L1 Node registration, Node verification, Node governance.\n 289 - 19:22 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's approval on Ch5 outline\n 290 - 19:07 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's approval on Ch5 outline\n 291 - 16:51 PM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's response on security layer questions\n 292 - 09:15 AM — Heartbeat: idle, awaiting Allan's review\n     ...","firstChangedLine":289},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773247147258}}
